FL,434,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1784468869
OL,3,CHosepipe ban announced for parts of
OL,4,Cwest Wales
OL,6,FThose caught using a hosepipe during a
OL,7,Fban can be subject to a fine up to
OL,8,F#1,000.
OL,10,FThe affected area stretches from
OL,11,FLlanon, Llangwyryfon and Cwm Ystwyth
OL,12,Fin Ceredigion, across to Crymych,
OL,13,FLlanfyrnach and Nevern in north
OL,14,FPembrokeshire, and into parts of north
OL,15,FCarmarthenshire, including Farmers,
OL,16,FPencader and Hermon.
OL,18,FThe restriction will begin at 10am,
OL,19,Fthe day before the six-week summer
OL,20,Fholiday period officially begins.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
