FL,434,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1784468869
OL,3,CHosepipe ban announced for parts of
OL,4,Cwest Wales
OL,6,FWelsh Water have imposed the ban
OL,7,Fduring the third and longest heatwave
OL,8,Fof the season as a result of higher
OL,9,Fdemands in drinking water.
OL,11,FDwr Cymru said demand has been at
OL,12,F"unprecedented levels" with around one
OL,13,Fbillion litres of drinking water being
OL,14,Fput into supply everyday in the last
OL,15,Fweek.
OL,17,FThe demand for water is up 20% more
OL,18,Fthan usual for this time of year and
OL,19,Fthe company said it is unable to
OL,20,Fsustain effectively treating the water.
OL,26,@sD@Bs{
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
