OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,434,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1784468869
OL,3,CHosepipe ban announced for parts of
OL,4,Cwest Wales
OL,6,FWelsh Water said it is taking
OL,7,F"extensive" measures to maintain
OL,8,Fsupplies, including water treatment,
OL,9,Fadditional movement across the
OL,10,Fnetwork, the reservoirs are "being
OL,11,Fkept as full as possible", increased
OL,12,Fattention to leaks, and all round
OL,13,Fhigher levels of support.
OL,15,FReservoirs are currently in a healthy
OL,16,Fposition but they are depleting faster
OL,17,Fthan they can be replenished.
OL,19,FKit Wilson, Chief Customer Officer
OL,20,Fsaid it was not an easy decision and
OL,21,Fhe understands frustration.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
