OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,434,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1784468869
OL,3,CHosepipe ban announced for parts of
OL,4,Cwest Wales
OL,6,FMr Wilson added: "After several weeks
OL,7,Fof unprecedented demand, they
OL,8,F(hosepipe bans) have become necessary
OL,9,Fto help protect essential water
OL,10,Fsupplies.
OL,12,F"Our teams have been working around
OL,13,Fthe clock".
OL,15,FHe continued: "The challenge is
OL,16,Fproducing, treating and moving enough
OL,17,Fdrinking water through the network
OL,18,Fquickly enough to meet this
OL,19,Fexceptional and sustained level of
OL,20,Fdemand.
OL,26,@pD@ApmpD@OpntD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/6
