OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,434,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1784468869
OL,3,CHosepipe ban announced for parts of
OL,4,Cwest Wales
OL,6,F"These restrictions are a temporary
OL,7,Femergency measure and will remain in
OL,8,Fplace only for as long as they are
OL,9,Fneeded. We would like to thank our
OL,10,Fcustomers for their understanding and
OL,11,Fsupport. By reducing non-essential
OL,12,Fwater use, everyone can help protect
OL,13,Fsupplies and reduce the risk of
OL,14,Ffurther disruption."
OL,16,FDwr Cymru says it will monitor the
OL,17,Fdemand for drinking water and weather
OL,18,Fconditions closely, and add that the
OL,19,Fban will be removed as soon as it is
OL,20,Fsuitable.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@TO]xD@Bs{
